net.finmath.montecarlo.process

Class ProcessEulerScheme

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.finmath.montecarlo.process.AbstractProcess
      • net.finmath.montecarlo.process.ProcessEulerScheme
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Cloneable, AbstractProcessInterface

    public class ProcessEulerScheme
extends AbstractProcess
    This class is an abstract base class to implement a multi-dimensional multi-factor Ito process. The dimension is called numberOfComponents here. The default for numberOfFactors is 1.
    Version:
    1.4
    Author:
    Christian Fries

      • clone

        public ProcessEulerScheme clone()
        Description copied from interface: AbstractProcessInterface
        Create and return a clone of this process. The clone is not tied to any model, but has the same process specification, that is, if the model is the same, it would generate the same paths.
